Articles.Content:
Canards are just front mounted tail surfaces, I have a few planes with more conventional layout and canards only at the back, but C7\'s stuff does make combat jets too easy to make.

@BamBam, yeah that\'ll work, you\'ll move the center of lift as well so watch for that.

Btw I find rudders are not much use as they make craft roll in an unwanted fashion, but that\'s just my preference ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
